data.description: Completely updated Little Bay Harbor condo! Peaceful Sawgrass Country Club lagoon location and views, including golf from the balcony! Rare oversized 2-car garage + storage. New bright, white kitchen and matching dry bar, wood shelving, built-ins, remote-controlled blinds, tile, wood & LVP flooring up and down (no carpet!), new & updated bathrooms, and custom closet shelving systems in the roomy walk-in closets. Plumbing and water heater are new. The condo association just completed balcony work, installing new membranes.  Community swimming pool is around the corner; beach access is across Ponte Vedra Blvd. at the Beach Club. Excellent restaurants & shops are close to this convenient location. It's an easy lifestyle here in Sawgrass Country Club! CC amenities available with membership.
